title: Narcopolis 2015 720p BluRay
description:
===================================================================================
Narcopolis is a futuristic thriller set in the near future where all classes of drugs have been legalized. Frank Grieves is a 'Dreck'| a roaming narc responsible for
keeping the black market dealers off the streets and the licenced drugs companies rich. When he discovers a rogue substance in an unidentified corpse| evidence
suggests that Ambro| the most powerful drug manufacturer of all| are conducting secret tests on an experimental narcotic. Grieves discovers a second victim - this
time alive - but she disappears and he is suddenly taken off the case by his superiors. As his options drain away| it's clear that legalization has come at a heavy
price. Is it too late to save the city?
===================================================================================
